Assignment no 1

Overview
Deployed all three applications using Kubernetes Deployment YAML files.

Applications Deployed
•	Nginx
•	Httpbin
•	Echoserver

Implementation Details
•	Created Kubernetes Deployment YAML files for all applications.
•	Configured resource requests and limits for containers.
•	Applied Kubernetes Services for application connectivity.
•	Added readiness probes to verify application availability before receiving traffic.
•	Added liveness probes to automatically restart unhealthy containers.
•	Used port forwarding commands in the terminal to access all three applications locally.
•	
Commands Used for Verification
Check Kubernetes Pods
kubectl get pods
Check Deployments
kubectl get deployments
Check Services
kubectl get svc


Verify Deployment Rollout Status
kubectl rollout status deployment/echoserver --timeout=120s

kubectl rollout status deployment/httpbin --timeout=120s
kubectl rollout status deployment/nginx-deployment --timeout=120s
Access Applications Using Port Forwarding
Nginx
kubectl port-forward svc/nginx 8080:80
Access:
http://localhost:8080
Echoserver
kubectl port-forward svc/echoserver 8081:80
Access:
http://localhost:8081
Httpbin
kubectl port-forward svc/httpbin 8082:8080
Access:
http://localhost:8082
